title: Why Microsoft, Amazon and Shopify All Fell on Monday
description: In this video, I will explain why Amazon (NASDAQ: AMZN), Microsoft (NASDAQ: MSFT), and Shopify (NYSE: SHOP) all fell on Monday while the broader market was green.  *Stock prices used were from the trading day of March 20, 2023.

title: Dow Jones Futures: First Republic Crashes On New Wall Street Rescue Talks; Fed Meeting Next
description: Dow Jones futures: First Republic crashed 47%, as JPMorgan and other big banks made new efforts to stabilize the troubled bank.

title: Market Highlights: ASX to bounce back, Goldman says risk-off, and 5 small caps to watch today
description: The ASX is set to bounce back this morning and recoup some of yesterday’s losses. First Republic Bank crashed 47% and has now lost 90%.
